docs.title: Alex's Documentation Deployment Test
docs.text:
This is a quick example of a documentation hub deployed via Material for MKDocs, that was deployed in ~30 minutes.

Changes made to the Github repo are automatically processed via Github Actions to be deployed to the main hosted site.

There is a wide range of customization options available, as described on the main Material for MKDocs Customization Page, so further CSS, Javascript, design, and layout options can be explored.
